  <h2>Prerequisites</h2> 
  <p>Before you can use the Smart Content Service, ensure the following to create an integration on Adobe I/O:<br /> </p> 
  <ul> 
   <li>An Adobe ID account that has administrator privileges for the organization.</li> 
   <li>The Smart Content Service service is enabled for your organization.</li> 
  </ul> 
  <p>To enable Enhanced Smart Tags, in addition to the above, also install <a href="/content/help/en/experience-manager/aem-releases-updates#main-pars_step_with_card_1987226281" target="_blank">AEM 6.4 latest service pack</a>.</p> 
  <h2>Obtain public certificate</h2> 
  <p>A public certificate allows you to authenticate your profile on Adobe I/O.<br /> </p> 
